A simple and lightweight real-time chat application built with **Node.js**, **Express**, and **Socket.IO**.  
Users can create or join rooms using a **room code** and a **maximum member limit**, making it ideal for quick private group chats.

ğŸ”— **Repository:** https://github.com/SaiKumar2121/chat-room

